<h3 data-path-to-node="32">Adaptability &amp; Typography</h3>
<p data-path-to-node="33">A premium mark must scale seamlessly from a digital favicon or a luxury pen to large-scale architectural signage. The mark retains its integrity in full color, solid black, or inverted.</p>
<p data-path-to-node="34">For the wordmark, I selected <strong data-path-to-node="34" data-index-in-node="29">Khand </strong>as font. The strong verticality and structural, angular letterforms offer a striking contrast to the organic curves of the brandmark, resulting in a modern, confident, and sophisticated lockup.</p>
<p> </p>
